    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>PASS. QUARANTINE. KILL</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You've been enlisted to run a Soviet checkpoint after a nuclear meltdown unleashes a viral mutagen. It's your job to inspect papers, spot lies, and judge twisted bodies while battling radiation, paranoia, and the deadly cost of every mistake.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Stamp Their Fate</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262820/extras/a6397612465185098e9f3e5408ca91de.poster.avif?t=1772197821\" width=1170 height=426 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262820/extras/a6397612465185098e9f3e5408ca91de.webm?t=1772197821\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262820/extras/a6397612465185098e9f3e5408ca91de.mp4?t=1772197821\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Pass, Quarantine, or Kill. </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every decision alters the town’s survival — and your own.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pass normal folks into town</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Quarantine the infected, but not too-far-gone</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Put those who-can't-be-helped out of their misery, or risk fates worse than death.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>INSPECT THE RESIDENTS OF SAPLAVI</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262820/extras/6b6bc34e6f848d14f220ee883f1ed2d6.poster.avif?t=1772197821\" width=1170 height=426 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262820/extras/6b6bc34e6f848d14f220ee883f1ed2d6.webm?t=1772197821\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262820/extras/6b6bc34e6f848d14f220ee883f1ed2d6.mp4?t=1772197821\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Analyze IDs, medical forms, permits, and forged papers under pressure.</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cross-analyze documents to see that the person isn't losing their identity.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Observe their tells. Are they hiding something? </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Observe physical anomalies, from the obvious tumors and rotting flesh, to the subtle hints in their behavior that they've turned and are hiding it.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>SURVIVE 30 DAYS AND NIGHTS IN HELL</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262820/extras/75d0f271ab5cadabe05f878f04cf1fe1.poster.avif?t=1772197821\" width=1170 height=426 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262820/extras/75d0f271ab5cadabe05f878f04cf1fe1.webm?t=1772197821\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262820/extras/75d0f271ab5cadabe05f878f04cf1fe1.mp4?t=1772197821\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Don't be soft. This is war.</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defend yourself from feral mutants</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Eliminate those who will become a threat tomorrow.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don't let others in town fall victim to the same fate. We are counting on you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>UNLEASH YOUR ARSENAL</strong> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262820/extras/b68d79000520d65f340e3bfe91e922a0.poster.avif?t=1772197821\" width=1170 height=426 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262820/extras/b68d79000520d65f340e3bfe91e922a0.webm?t=1772197821\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262820/extras/b68d79000520d65f340e3bfe91e922a0.mp4?t=1772197821\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Manage your measly salary to purchase supplies, gear and upgrades to your booth.</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Purchase tools and supplies from the tool locker</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade your weapons and defense systems</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Manage your very, very limited resources. Any purchase comes out of your salary.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>AT LEAST YOU'RE NOT ALONE (CO-OP)</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262820/extras/50392a890a493c0455d93894d436be62.poster.avif?t=1772197821\" width=1170 height=426 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262820/extras/50392a890a493c0455d93894d436be62.webm?t=1772197821\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262820/extras/50392a890a493c0455d93894d436be62.mp4?t=1772197821\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Work together (or sabotage each other) as paranoia spreads inside the booth.</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Split the work-load as one person analyzes documents while the other scans their physical symptoms</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Drink vodka, smoke cigarettes and find a moment to just chill between the heaviness of ethical dilemmas </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Permadeath? Nah. We just call in a replacement if one of you dies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul>",
